# PROJECT DETAILS

| Item                  | Details                                                   |
|-----------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------|
| Project Title         | End to End CI/CD Pipeline (Jenkins + SonarQube + Nexus + Tomcat) |
| Domains               | DevOps / CI-CD Automation                                |
| Application Type      | Java Maven Application (.War)                            |
| Source Code Repository| https://github.com/suffixscope/maven-web-app             |
| Deployment Target     | Apache Tomcat (War Deployment)                           |
| Cloud Platform        | AWS EC2                                                  |
| Pipeline Tool         | Jenkins                                                  |
| Code Quality          | SonarQube                                                |
| Artifact Repository   | Nexus Repository Manager                                 |

Implement a complete CI/CD workflow for a Maven-based Java web application to:

- Automatically pull source code from GitHub  
- Build and package the project using Maven  
- Perform static code analysis with SonarQube  
- Store the generated `.war` artifact in Nexus Repository Manager  
- Deploy the application seamlessly to Apache Tomcat  
- Verify successful deployment by accessing the application in a browser
